"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"We live in a world of advertising. As potential consumers, we are endlessly bombarded with all kinds of product or service information from various media including newspapers, magazines, television, radio, posters and Internet, etc. Advertising provides a valuable service to society and its members, because it defines for consumers the meaning and the role of products, services, and institutions. It indicates the difference that exists between brands of products and alternative services, as well as the distinguishing characteristics of companies and institutions. Advertising also tells the consumer what a specific product, brand or service should do when it is used and thus helps him or her to understand and evaluate experience with the products and services that he or she uses. On the other hand, by making people aware of products, service and ideas, advertising promotes sales and profits. Finally, advertising is one of the major forces that are helping improve the standard of living around the world. Combined with all these communicational, marketing and social functions. Advertising becomes indispensable in the modern world.\",\"timestamp\":1638955685,\"title\":\"We live in a world of advertising\"},\"digest\":\"g0hWbwjr3OV0GFDlP_N3zZQh3fWuoexlbsPklnfuiIk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xA797Ad68D67d854eb79E816E5Eb8b2fc6244692B\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FStipDXzqblY4w2uLGHjc-uPtNOheHBmoRcQ36Gdy58\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Q3Ru0Is-i5Kcb-C6-WPqSClTVR4KAVxjVrDb5uiZAMo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"RalBj0pKLnXQ8Ni5FC1g04J_7aBhGEGNcICteWf_JfwG1rdxKfddbjLLcaUdyMoz2pobKIU0XY-j1ocqnQ0QXg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x5ed77d9f45bce1621774930734a3e2ba604dc9c1cce5f9b4042539a6237619884130a1f78ba83b1a1193a4b686efea35207d6c04a27a910c243f611f95a6e39f1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"